modName: ENB for I Cant Believe Its Not An ENB
descriptionHtml:
First.Sorry for my bad english.

This Enb is for low-middle pc videocards ( like my - GF650Ti Boost).
Perfomance with this preset + I Cant Believe Its Not An ENB in my Skyrim is practically always -60fps.
(All ultra settings)
Except castle Volkihar - (i dont know why) fps lowers to 45-50 ,and Riften -50fps min.
------------------
Req.
Climates Of Tamriel
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17802/?
Enhanced Lights and FX
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27043/?
optional sunsprite shader by Kyokushinoyama.
from Realvision Optional files.
Recommended :
Imaginator
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13049/?
WATER - Water And Terrain Enhancement Redux
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13268/?


Instructions:
1. Open SkyrimPrefs.ini located in My DocumentMy GamesSkyrim


2. Find the line,


bFloatPointRenderTarget=1
bTreesReceiveShadows=1
bDrawLandShadows=1
bShadowsOnGrass=1

Download latest ENB v 0.246
http://forum.skyrimtuner.com/viewtopic.php?f=16&t=99

Copy d3d9.dll and enbhost.exe un paste files where the TESV.exe is.

Download
I Cant Believe Its Not An ENB
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/48554/?
Install all. Except - d3d9.dll!!!


Unzip and copy all files from - ENB for I Cant Believe Its Not An ENB .zip
into your Skyrim folder .

Done.

All credit goes to:

The develpoer of ENB, Boris Vorontsov : http://enbdev.com/
anamorfus - Enhanced Lights and FX
ElSopa- I Cant Believe Its Not An ENB
jjc71- Climates Of Tamriel
Kyokushinoyama- Sunsprite shader .
